title: Lamar Jackson and the Ravens Run Wild Against the Patriots, and More Week 9 Reactions | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
The Baltimore Ravens are playing the most interesting football in the NFL, but is their success sustainable? (0:25) Then, Stock Up on Andy Reid’s Patrick Mahomes–less success, Deshaun Watson’s weekly heroics, and Russell Wilson thrusting the Seahawks into contention (17:00), and Stock Down on the catastrophic Bears and the Packers, before throwing a challenge flag on the Jets foiling the Dolphins’ tank (41:45).
Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
